# HR Compliance Hub - Application Description

## Overview
HR Compliance Hub is a comprehensive human resources and business management system designed to streamline HR operations, ensure compliance, track key performance indicators, and manage employee-related tasks efficiently.

## Core Features

### 1. Dashboard
- Overview of key metrics and statistics
- Task completion rates
- Compliance scores
- Recent notifications
- High-priority items tracking

### 2. Document Management
- Secure document storage and organization
- Document expiry tracking
- Version control
- Document status tracking (Active/Archived)
- Export capabilities
- File upload/download functionality

### 3. Compliance Management
- Task tracking and management
- Priority-based task organization
- Progress tracking with completion percentages
- Due date monitoring
- Task status updates
- Automated notifications for upcoming deadlines

### 4. Employee Hub
- Employee profile management
- Leave management system
  - Leave requests
  - Approval workflow
  - Leave balance tracking
- Document storage per employee
- Status tracking (Active/On Leave/Terminated)
- Employee information export

### 5. Handbooks & Policies
- Digital handbook management
- Policy categorization
- Section-based organization
- Easy updates and versioning
- Category-based filtering
- Quick access to important sections

### 6. Payroll Management
- Payroll record tracking
- Payment scheduling
- Payment status monitoring
- CSV export functionality
- Payment history
- Salary tracking
- Payment processing status

### 7. KPI Tracker
- Interactive performance metrics tracking
- Real-time data visualization
- Key metrics monitoring:
  - Lead generation
  - Revenue tracking
  - Project management
  - Expense monitoring
- Features:
  - Data entry and editing
  - Historical data tracking
  - Multiple chart types
  - Data export functionality
  - Customizable timeframes
  - Category management
  - Target vs. actual comparison
- Target users:
  - Marketing agencies
  - Freelancers
  - Solopreneurs
  - Business managers

### 8. FAQ Knowledge Base
- Categorized FAQ sections
- Search functionality
- Easy-to-navigate Q&A format
- Categories:
  - Employment
  - Payroll
  - Leave
  - Health & Safety

## Technical Features
- Dark/Light mode support
- Responsive design
- Search functionality across all modules
- Data export capabilities
- Notification system
- Secure data storage
- User-friendly interface
- Interactive charts and visualizations
- Local data persistence
- Dynamic data updates

